## Main User Flows

1. **Contract Upload Flow**: Drag-drop file → ProcessingBar in TopNav → New workbench item (Pioneer Systems)
2. **Customer Link Flow**: Click workbench item → CustomerLinkModal → Match/create customer
3. **Contract Processing Flow**: Process contract → Customer360Page with sections (Summary, Account, Addresses, Terms, Products, Invoice)
